title: Eric Bibb - Live At The Basement - DVDRip  (AC3 Audio) [akhiugo]
description:
Over the last 25 years the stage of Sydney's legendary 'Basement' night club has been graced by Jazz & Blues music's international elite.

The night Eric Bibb came to town was a pearler. Original tunes, beautifully crafted, a blend of heart, mind and humour which had the full house enthralled.

This beautiful recording will put you right there in the moment with Eric & Dave Bronze weaving the kind of spell only live music can.



Recorded live at the Basement Night Club, Sydney, Australia 2002.
